{"tid":849044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB裁員約150人　佔現職員工4%","createTime":"2018-10-05T11:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T14:50:45.000Z","uid":41404,"like":239,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"40991c87fb36b52e40c376d2713f2acecb6d58f3","tid":849044,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"無綫電視宣布裁員約150人，分別來自TVB周刊、製作統籌部、美術分部及非戲劇製作，佔現職員工4%。<br />\n<br />\n無綫表示，為應對業務環境及營運需要的轉變，TVB周刊的印刷本會被網上版取代，另外由於增加實景拍攝導致廠景拍攝減少，將關閉其中一個戲劇錄影廠，而非戲劇製作亦精簡運作。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，裁減職位是一個困難的決定，但由於公司需要面對業務環境及營運需要的轉變，會繼續投資提升製作，以及將資源投放於發展中和新的業務。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421525-20181005.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421525-20181005.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=5bacb0e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421525-20181005.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=63c2cfe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421525-20181005.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5c786f413c4589664abd9b61dbdff6f81448c9a6","tid":849044,"uid":13592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"陰9公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e32d6d84904b44220d74523642f05f954df2f8","tid":849044,"uid":93998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"5662e1c3e47641da9e4b018bbfd9d439d6faac42","tid":849044,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣.jpg"},{"pid":"10277685c13809786aedab755f90fa034c0fd150","tid":849044,"uid":3122,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"3千幾人咁撚勁<img src